{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=e602408a305a9c42e2cfaf0d5a59136c&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F8b82b9014a90f6032d6e366b3112b31bb151edc4.jpg","summary":"湖南财政经济学院地处湖南省长沙市，是一所由湖南省人民政府主办、湖南省教育厅主管、湖南省财政厅协管的全日制本科院校。学院前身是1933年创办的“厚生会计讲习所”，1993年更名为“湖南财经高等专科学校”，2010年3月经教育部批准，学校升格为普通本科院校。经过多年的建设，学校已经发展成为一所以经济、管理学科为主体，办学特色鲜明、教育竞争力不断增强的省属财经本科院校。截至2016年7月，学院总占地面积760多亩；设有12个教学单位，共开办25个本科专业、3个专科专业；有教职工645人，其中正高职称教师74人，副教授151人；在校学生1万余人。截至2015年底，为社会培养了5万多名财经管理专门人才。","tags":["财经类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1933","所在地区":"长沙市岳麓区枫林二路139号","院校隶属":"湖南省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=3788e23c56efeb594abfcb1a797bf513&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3623057539%2C735882147%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=f9cf9542ee5a3f84bb6ff5cedc37f6c6&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3660234909%2C766079105%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=7d58288453d367ba649e52eadfffba9c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3710431306%2C894617043%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=3b333ebd337f2e53bb6b875c35d9b155&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3549695694%2C3991207011%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=2cb1e880355d5fce1c17362ab4b3ae8d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3567018442%2C4054222927%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_